create workdlows/name.yaml
and write the yaml file all steps n all ,basically write deployment workflows
then go tot he eas expo dashboard -- connect github there and search for repo and connect thru the repo
during repo connection u can specify the specific path inside the repo

then in bottom there is button for get started simply click ans start that time it will provide multiple command run that locally

after successful connectioon u just need to push code then automatic workflow will run in the expo environment

u need 14,to 12 testers(people) jiske phone me app installed rhe and wo use krte rhe daily basis pe 14 days ke liye tb approve hoga

how to publish the app
1.create production build by running command that will prepeare in expo
2.download that (it will be in the aab format)
3.go to google play console dashboard
4.and create new app uplod your production build

